messages.message: Hi team - created an app to extract a table from this document type (top left screenshot is the correct extraction of the table). When I ran through 20 different docs of the same type I got highly inconsistent results. Some say "There is only one table in the given text" without extracting the table, majority say "there are no tables in the given text", and two that did extract tables, but the tables were very incorrect (rows & columns bleeding into each other). Attaching documents below
I believe that we are integrating the long table extraction in Build with 23.39 release. We should see better results post that for such scenarios. @Eric Han and @Bastiane can confirm.
